Yep, bal_002.nes with the noise sounds fine on the NES too.  Looks like you forgot to clear the name/attrib table.  Oh well, that won't affect the sound anyways.<br /><br />For the pitch bends, if anyone wants to do a slow or shallow one, it would almost have to be a lot finer than a semitone.  Like playing a guitar, it's probably more common to bend the string and stay in the same fret instead of sliding up/down the fretboard, heheh.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=10">Memblers</a> — Wed Nov 10, 2004 9:17 pm</p><hr />
